{"tid":1241654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我知大家都開始攰啦","createTime":"2019-06-18T19:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T19:11:00.000Z","uid":131125,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92e801769b6311b48427644a6e1be614290618b9","tid":1241654,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:02:25.000Z","msg":"再加上壓力又大，對家做啲事又荒撚謬<br />\n所以先會不停恥笑對家<br />\n毅進制好condom仔好<br />\n果堆死唔斷氣九唔搭八嘅記招都好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但仲有最少五個人等緊我地救架<br />\n香港都等緊我地救架</span></span><br />\n如果再咁鬆散落去無人幫到手架啦<br />\n鄺囝都係有咩事趕去幫拖架咋<br />\n黃之鋒啱啱出黎，而且最多都係做下精神領袖出句聲幫下手架咋<br />\n同上個禮拜一樣，成唔成事係靠我地架<br />\n<br />\n上個禮拜都唔叫成功<br />\n但最少我地有向住我地嘅方向做到野出黎<br />\n同埋有更多人關注引起更多嘅問題同發現<br />\n但621我地連向邊度行都未知啊<br />\n好似勇武到底應唔應該繼續升級武力<br />\n定掟下蛋算呢<br />\n不合作運動應唔應該繼續<br />\n定係要顧民意而唔做呢<br />\n<br />\n比起上個禮拜一鼓作氣不停出擊<br />\n我地而家好似咩都未準備咁<br />\n我都係一個少發言嘅連登仔<br />\n但我唔想見住呢次就咁慢慢無哂希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩大家集中返去啲621討論post<br />\n或者推下啲叫人醒嘅post<br />\n製造返個風氣同氣氛出黎先</span><br />\n<br />\n希望今個禮拜唔再發噩夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3f8432625f65b9fc5ed6b400dee689cf6807bd","tid":1241654,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:03:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3feb2b52c7f01a3d98816bc2089f27fce79362a4","tid":1241654,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:04:02.000Z","msg":"唉  香港人加油"},{"pid":"21eb19600032c0f3281e940369a054f198287891","tid":1241654,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:04:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d673544638a086fd6f08cd36b22eb3f6cb69e5ad","tid":1241654,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:05:48.000Z","msg":"開垃圾post 全部封鎖咗"},{"pid":"4867f37f14a83bf880d498608c12457261490495","tid":1241654,"uid":131125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:06:14.000Z","msg":"推多兩推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0612812ddaba0b7ed9fe7db8b176ada406809d","tid":1241654,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:09:23.000Z","msg":"連續兩個星期日行 609-610之間同612又咁 又有義士走咗 又要聽港支政府又日日廢up 其實真係好辛苦 太多嘢發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dc3802a73014efecae6a8d98608946c69eefa4","tid":1241654,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T19:11:00.000Z","msg":"不過休息多陣好喇 一齊諗吓621<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}